# Workflow Loops Benchmark — git policy
#
# Keep `results/report-NNN.md` (history of benchmark runs is a project asset).
# Drop `results/report-NNN/` artefact directories (per-case session logs + raw
# pytest stdout: high volume, low signal-per-byte).

results/report-*/
!results/report-*.md

# Local pytest cache
__pycache__/
.pytest_cache/
